Brenda Elder https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Brenda_Elder 0 Brenda Elder (born 1938) is an English actress, best remembered for her recurring role as Elsie Seddon, the mother of Sally Webster, in Coronation Street from 1986 to 1997.
